This page is meant to give darcs users
and developers a way to flesh out their ideas.

Since the ideas are just that and not necessarily finished or accepted proposals, just because an idea is described here doesn't mean it's something that should or will be implemented.

Any specific feature requests should be logged on the
[bugtracker](http://bugs.darcs.net)

